    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with plenty of potential. This vehicle is being offered as a budget-friendly option for someone looking for basic mobility, a project, or a practical spare. It shows its age and wear, but it presents a strong value opportunity at this price point for a buyer who appreciates honest, no-nonsense motoring. If you want inexpensive entry into ownership without overpaying, this is worth a look.",
