    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Clean title and priced to move, this is a great budget-friendly car for someone who wants affordable wheels or a solid little project. It\u2019s not perfect, but it has plenty of potential and would suit a handy owner, first-time buyer, or anyone needing basic transportation without spending a fortune. Honest value, straightforward sale, and a chance to get into a car at a very accessible price.",
