      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Clean, honest project with strong bones and a drivetrain that still feels eager. Starts, runs, and moves, with a willing engine, solid torque delivery, and the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes this a great candidate for a budget daily, weekend fixer, or parts-savvy enthusiast build. Shows age and needs cosmetic and general reconditioning, but it presents as a usable platform with plenty of upside for someone who knows their way around maintenance. If you want an affordable car with real potential instead of a total basket case, this is worth a look.",
      "price": 7900.0,
