      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a scrappy, dependable companion with plenty of story left to tell. It\u2019s ideal for someone who sees opportunity where others see a weekend project: a practical runabout, a budget-friendly backup, or a rewarding restoration canvas. If you want something inexpensive with real personality and the potential to earn its keep, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 4900.0,
