      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers dependable transportation value for the right buyer. It shows its age cosmetically, but it remains a practical option for commuting, a first car, or a project opportunity. If you're looking for an inexpensive way to get on the road without overpaying, this is a smart chance to buy at an accessible price.",
