    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Honest, affordable runabout that\u2019s perfect for someone needing simple, no-nonsense transport or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s not a show car, but it\u2019s got character and still has plenty to offer the right buyer. If you want something budget-friendly from a straightforward seller, this could be a great fit. Priced to sell and worth a look.",
